o pursue careers in astronomy and space science.\n","i-heroicons-rocket-launch",{"title":104,"description":105,"icon":106},"Our Vision","To be Sri Lanka's leading alumni-based astronomical organization, bridging the gap between professional astronomy and public education while preserving and advancing the scientific heritage of Ananda College for future generations.\n","i-heroicons-eye",{"title":108,"items":109},"Our Milestones",[110,118,125,132],{"position":111,"date":112,"company":113},"Ananda College Founded",1886,{"name":114,"logo":115,"url":116,"color":117},"Ananda College","i-ph-graduation-cap","https://anandacollege.edu.lk","#F59E42",{"position":119,"date":120,"company":121},"Anandian Astronomical Association Founded",1998,{"name":122,"logo":123,"url":23,"color":124},"AAA","i-ph-telescope","#4F46E5",{"position":126,"date":127,"company":128},"OAAA Founded",2004,{"name":129,"logo":130,"url":23,"color":131},"OAAA","i-ph-users-three","#00DC82",{"position":133,"date":134,"company":135},"OAAA Affiliates with OBA",2025,{"name":136,"logo":137,"url":23,"color":138},"ACOBA","i-ph-link","#5E6AD2",{"title":30,"description":31,"officials":140},[141,142,143,144,145,146,147],{"name":34,"role":35,"image":36},{"name":38,"role":39,"image":40},{"name":42,"role":43,"image":44},{"name":46,"role":47,"image":48},{"name":50,"role":51,"image":52},{"name":54,"role":55,"image":56},{"name":58,"role":59,"image":60},{"title":27,"description":28},[150,158,164],{"quote":151,"author":152},"Our kids may not have seen the ocean yet, but today they got to see the stars. As a parent, Iâ€™m truly grateful.",{"name":153,"description":154,"avatar":155},"Kumuduni Perera","Parent, Participate Astro Kids Programme (Kalagama, Nikaweratiya)",{"src":156,"alt":157},"","Dr. Samantha Perera",{"quote":159,"author":160},"As a former student of Ananda College, OAAA's mentorship program helped me pursue my passion for astrophysics. Their guidance and resources were instrumental in my academic journey.",{"name":161,"description":162,"avatar":163},"Kavinda Silva","PhD Candidate in Astrophysics",{"src":156,"alt":161},{"quote":165,"author":166},"OAAA's public stargazing events have become a highlight in Sri Lanka's science education calendar. They make astronomy accessible and exciting for everyone.",{"name":167,"description":168,"avatar":169},"Prof. Nimal Gunawardena","Director, Sri Lanka Astronomical Society",{"src":156,"alt":167},{"title":171,"description":172,"categories":173},"Frequently Asked Questions","Common questions about the Old Anandians' Astronomical Association",[174,186,198],{"title":175,"questions":176},"General",[177,180,183],{"label":178,"content":179},"What is OAAA?","The Old Anandians' Astronomical Association (OAAA) is an organization that unites alumni of Ananda College, Colombo, who share a passion for astronomy. We promote astronomical education and scientific inquiry among Anandians and the broader Sri Lankan community.\n",{"label":181,"content":182},"How can I join OAAA?","To join OAAA, you must be an alumnus of Ananda College, Colombo. You can contact us through our official channels or attend one of our events to learn more about membership requirements and the application process.\n",{"label":184,"content":185},"What activities does OAAA organize?","OAAA organizes various activities including public stargazing events, astronomy workshops, educational seminars, telescope demonstrations, and collaborative projects with schools and universities to promote astronomical education.\n",{"title":187,"questions":188},"Events & Programs",[189,192,195],{"label":190,"content":191},"Are OAAA events open to the public?","Yes, many of our events are open to the public, especially our stargazing sessions and educational workshops. We believe in making astronomy accessible to everyone, regardless of their background or experience level.\n",{"label":193,"content":194},"Do I need my own telescope to participate?","No, you don't need your own telescope. OAAA provides telescopes and equipment for our events. However, if you have your own equipment, you're welcome to bring it along to our stargazing sessions.\n",{"label":196,"content":197},"How often does OAAA organize events?","We organize events regularly throughout the year, with major stargazing sessions typically scheduled around significant astronomical events like meteor showers, eclipses, and planetary alignments.\n",{"title":199,"questions":200},"Education & Outreach",[201,204,207],{"label":202,"content":203},"Does OAAA offer educational programs for schools?","Yes, we actively collaborate with schools to provide astronomy education programs. We visit schools to conduct workshops, provide telescope demonstrations, and inspire young minds to explore the wonders of the universe.\n",{"label":205,"content":206},"Can students participate in OAAA research projects?","We encourage student participation in our research and observational projects. Students can contribute to citizen science initiatives and learn practical astronomy skills through hands-on experience.\n",{"label":208,"content":209},"How does OAAA support aspiring astronomers?","OAAA provides mentorship programs, educational resources, and networking opportunities for aspiring astronomers. We connect students with experienced professionals and provide guidance for pursuing careers in astronomy and related fields.\n",{"title":108,"items":211},[212,214,216,218],{"position":111,"date":112,"company":213},{"name":114,"logo":115,"url":116,"color":117},{"position":119,"date":120,"company":215},{"name":122,"logo":123,"url":23,"color":124},{"position":126,"date":127,"company":217},{"name":129,"logo":130,"url":23,"color":131},{"position":133,"date":134,"company":219},{"name":136,"logo":137,"url":23,"color":138},"yml",{"title":171,"description":172,"categories":222},[223,228,233],{"title":175,"questions":224},[225,226,227],{"label":178,"content":179},{"label":181,"content":182},{"label":184,"content":185},{"title":187,"questi